 《惊声尖叫 7》正在与《忌日快乐》导演合作https://www.nme.com/news/film/scream-7-in-the-works-with-happy-death-day-director-3477470?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=scream-7-in-the-与忌日快乐导演合作Surej SinghThu, 03 Aug 2023 06:05:07 +0000 Film NewsNews https://www.nme.com/?p=3477470 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/Scream_2022_Reboot.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="尖叫" decoding="async" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/Scream_2022_Reboot.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/Scream_2022_Reboot-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/Scream_2022_Reboot-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/Scream_2022_Reboot-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/Scream_2022_Reboot-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/Scream_2022_Reboot-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>由于好莱坞编剧和演员正在进行罢工，目前尚不清楚珍娜·奥尔特加和其他演员是否会签约出演这部电影</p><p><a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/scream-7-in-the-works-with-happy-death-day-director-3477470">与《忌日快乐》导演合作的《惊声尖叫 7》后，</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/Scream_2022_Reboot.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="尖叫" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/Scream_2022_Reboot.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/Scream_2022_Reboot-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/Scream_2022_Reboot-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/Scream_2022_Reboot-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/Scream_2022_Reboot-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/Scream_2022_Reboot-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/films/scream"><em>《惊声尖叫》</em></a>系列的第七部目前正在制作中，由<em>《忌日快乐》</em>导演克里斯托弗·兰登执导。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/film-reviews/scream-6-review-ghostface-jenna-ortega-3409588">《惊声尖叫 VI》评论：穿越不夜城的噩梦般的惊险之旅</a></strong></li></ul><p>据<a href="https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/movies/movie-news/christopher-landon-to-direct-scream-7-1235549639/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>《好莱坞报道》</em></a>报道， <em>《惊声尖叫 7》</em>将标志着兰登在该系列电影中的首次亮相，接替了马特·贝蒂内利-奥尔平和泰勒·吉列的职务，他们曾执导 2022 年的<em>《惊声尖叫 5》</em>和今年的<a href="https://www.nme.com/films/scream-vi"><em>《惊声尖叫 6》</em></a> 。</p><p>据报道，贝蒂内利-奥尔平和吉列仍将与查德·维莱拉一起担任<em>《惊声尖叫 7》的</em>执行制片人。据报道，贝蒂内利-奥尔皮恩和吉列从<em>《惊声尖叫 7》</em>中辞职，为环球影业制作一部原创恐怖电影，但由于<a href="https://www.nme.com/en_au/news/film/how-long-will-the-hollywood-actors-strike-last-3473447">好莱坞正在进行的编剧和演员罢工，该电影</a>被叫停。</p><p> <em>《惊声尖叫 5》</em>和<em>《惊声尖叫 6》</em>系列电影获得了软重启，同时也作为原版电影的续集。演员阵容由<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/jenna-ortega">珍娜·奥尔特加</a>、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/film-interviews/melissa-barrera-interview-carmen-paul-mescal-scream-3450231">梅丽莎·巴雷拉</a>和梅森·古丁领衔。据<em>THR</em>报道，三位演员尚未签约<em>《惊声尖叫 7》</em> ，但预计一旦好莱坞罢工结束，他们就会签约。 </p><figure id="attachment_3383820" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3383820" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-3383820" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/Scream_6_Ghostface.jpg" alt="尖叫" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/Scream_6_Ghostface.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/Scream_6_Ghostface-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/Scream_6_Ghostface-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/Scream_6_Ghostface-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/Scream_6_Ghostface-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/Scream_6_Ghostface-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3383820" class="wp-caption-text">鬼面在《惊声尖叫 VI》中回归。图片来源：派拉蒙</figcaption></figure><p>克里斯托弗·兰登以编剧和导演惊悚片和喜剧恐怖片而闻名，例如《<em>忌日快乐</em>》、 <em>《僵尸启示录</em><em>童军指南</em>》、 <em>《忌日快乐 2U》</em> 、《<em>怪奇</em>》和<em>《我们有鬼》</em> 。他还担任<em>《超自然活动》</em>系列的编剧。</p><p> <em>《惊声尖叫 VI》</em>在今年早些时候发布时获得了 <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/film-reviews/scream-6-review-ghostface-jenna-ortega-3409588">四星评价</a>。 <em>NME</em>的 Alex Flood 写道：“ <em>《惊声尖叫 VI》</em>并不完美：不断的元参考（过去的杀手、系列的‘规则’）在去年的重启中感觉很有创意，但在这里变得令人厌烦。还有一个令人困惑的次要情节，围绕着山姆压抑的想要效仿她父亲（比利·卢米斯，最初的鬼脸）的愿望，她的父亲出现在幻觉中，告诉她去杀人。再加上通常的阐述环节，让观众了解最新的情节，但又让人感觉像是 Z 世代的<em>波洛</em>，这一切都可能会让你感到紧张。幸运的是，这就是纯粹的、血腥的快乐，你会因为太专注而没有注意到。也许更多的恐怖坏人<em>应该</em>搬到纽约？”</p><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/scream-7-in-the-works-with-happy-death-day-director-3477470">与《忌日快乐》导演合作的《惊声尖叫 7》后，</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
